{
  "video_id": "POHYyP4EbzE",
  "title": "What your smart devices know (and share) about you | Kashmir Hill and Surya Mattu",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12912.0,
      "end_time": 15470.0,
      "text": "Kashmir Hill: So for my birthday last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15710.0,
      "end_time": 17640.0,
      "text": "my husband got me an Amazon Echo."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17595.0,
      "end_time": 19134.0,
      "text": "I was kind of shocked, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19159.0,
      "end_time": 22393.0,
      "text": "because we both work in privacy and security."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22417.0,
      "end_time": 23753.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24688.0,
      "end_time": 28770.0,
      "text": "And this was a device that would sit in the middle of our home"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28101.0,
      "end_time": 29537.0,
      "text": "with a microphone on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29561.0,
      "end_time": 31210.0,
      "text": "constantly listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31696.0,
      "end_time": 32950.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not alone, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32974.0,
      "end_time": 35855.0,
      "text": "According to a survey by NPR and Edison Research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35879.0,
      "end_time": 39958.0,
      "text": "one in six American adults now has a smart speaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39982.0,
      "end_time": 42863.0,
      "text": "which means that they have a virtual assistant at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42887.0,
      "end_time": 44850.0,
      "text": "Like, that&#39;s wild."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44109.0,
      "end_time": 48225.0,
      "text": "The future, or the future dystopia, is getting here fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48778.0,
      "end_time": 53285.0,
      "text": "Beyond that, companies are offering us all kinds of internet-connected devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53309.0,
      "end_time": 58277.0,
      "text": "There are smart lights, smart locks, smart toilets, smart toys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58301.0,
      "end_time": 59612.0,
      "text": "smart sex toys."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60323.0,
      "end_time": 63140.0,
      "text": "Being smart means the device can connect to the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63380.0,
      "end_time": 64214.0,
      "text": "it can gather data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64238.0,
      "end_time": 66140.0,
      "text": "and it can talk to its owner."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66966.0,
      "end_time": 69679.0,
      "text": "But once your appliances can talk to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69704.0,
      "end_time": 71848.0,
      "text": "who else are they going to be talking to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72331.0,
      "end_time": 73696.0,
      "text": "I wanted to find out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73720.0,
      "end_time": 77108.0,
      "text": "so I went all-in and turned my one-bedroom apartment in San Francisco"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77132.0,
      "end_time": 78481.0,
      "text": "into a smart home."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78800.0,
      "end_time": 81890.0,
      "text": "I even connected our bed to the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82505.0,
      "end_time": 85807.0,
      "text": "As far as I know, it was just measuring our sleeping habits."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86490.0,
      "end_time": 88571.0,
      "text": "I can now tell you that the only thing worse"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88595.0,
      "end_time": 90382.0,
      "text": "than getting a terrible night&#39;s sleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90406.0,
      "end_time": 92823.0,
      "text": "is to have your smart bed tell you the next day"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92847.0,
      "end_time": 95902.0,
      "text": "that you \"missed your goal and got a low sleep score.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95927.0,
      "end_time": 97307.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97331.0,
      "end_time": 98768.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like, \"Thanks, smart bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98792.0,
      "end_time": 101308.0,
      "text": "As if I didn&#39;t already feel like shit today.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101332.0,
      "end_time": 102485.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102509.0,
      "end_time": 107450.0,
      "text": "All together, I installed 18 internet-connected devices in my home."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107690.0,
      "end_time": 109307.0,
      "text": "I also installed a Surya."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109331.0,
      "end_time": 110712.0,
      "text": "Surya Mattu: Hi, I&#39;m Surya."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110736.0,
      "end_time": 111934.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111958.0,
      "end_time": 114902.0,
      "text": "I monitored everything the smart home did."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114926.0,
      "end_time": 118855.0,
      "text": "I built a special router that let me look at all the network activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118879.0,
      "end_time": 121809.0,
      "text": "You can think of my router sort of like a security guard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121833.0,
      "end_time": 123966.0,
      "text": "compulsively logging all the network packets"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 123990.0,
      "end_time": 126360.0,
      "text": "as they entered and left the smart home."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 126610.0,
      "end_time": 128815.0,
      "text": "KH: Surya and I are both journalists, he&#39;s not my husband,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 128839.0,
      "end_time": 130514.0,
      "text": "we just work together at Gizmodo."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 130538.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131928.0,
      "text": "SM: Thank you for clarifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131952.0,
      "end_time": 133353.0,
      "text": "The devices Kashmir bought --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133378.0,
      "end_time": 135700.0,
      "text": "we were interested in understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135940.0,
      "end_time": 137204.0,
      "text": "what they were saying to their manufacturers."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 137229.0,
      "end_time": 139291.0,
      "text": "But we were also interested in understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139315.0,
      "end_time": 141685.0,
      "text": "what the home&#39;s digital emissions look like"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141709.0,
      "end_time": 143974.0,
      "text": "to the internet service provider."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143998.0,
      "end_time": 146840.0,
      "text": "We were seeing what the ISP could see, but more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 146864.0,
      "end_time": 148450.0,
      "text": "what they could sell."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148690.0,
      "end_time": 150212.0,
      "text": "KH: We ran the experiment for two months."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150236.0,
      "end_time": 151403.0,
      "text": "In that two months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 151427.0,
      "end_time": 154304.0,
      "text": "there wasn&#39;t a single hour of digital silence in the house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 154328.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "not even when we went away for a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156284.0,
      "end_time": 157458.0,
      "text": "SM: Yeah, it&#39;s so true."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157482.0,
      "end_time": 160498.0,
      "text": "Based on the data, I knew when you guys woke up and went to bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160522.0,
      "end_time": 162560.0,
      "text": "I even knew when Kashmir brushed her teeth."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 162585.0,
      "end_time": 164609.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to out your brushing habits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 164633.0,
      "end_time": 168262.0,
      "text": "but let&#39;s just say it was very clear to me when you were working from home."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 168286.0,
      "end_time": 171498.0,
      "text": "KH: Uh, I think you just outed them to, like, a lot of people here."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171522.0,
      "end_time": 173868.0,
      "text": "SM: Don&#39;t be embarrassed, it&#39;s just metadata."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174472.0,
      "end_time": 177615.0,
      "text": "I knew when you turned on your TV and how long you watched it for."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 177639.0,
      "end_time": 179268.0,
      "text": "Fun fact about the Hill household:"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179292.0,
      "end_time": 181860.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t watch a lot of television,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181110.0,
      "end_time": 183378.0,
      "text": "but when they do, it&#39;s usually in binge mode."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 183402.0,
      "end_time": 186180.0,
      "text": "Favorite shows include \"Difficult People\" and \"Party Down.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186205.0,
      "end_time": 188244.0,
      "text": "KH: OK, you&#39;re right, I loved \"Party Down.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 188268.0,
      "end_time": 190815.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a great show, and you should definitely watch it."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190839.0,
      "end_time": 193283.0,
      "text": "But \"Difficult People\" was all my husband, Trevor."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193307.0,
      "end_time": 196910.0,
      "text": "And Trevor was actually a little upset that you knew about his binges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196934.0,
      "end_time": 200268.0,
      "text": "because even though he&#39;d been the one to connect the TV to the router,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 200292.0,
      "end_time": 202739.0,
      "text": "he forgot that the TV was watching us."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203109.0,
      "end_time": 206402.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually not the first time that our TV has spied on us."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 206426.0,
      "end_time": 208125.0,
      "text": "The company that made it, VIZIO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 208149.0,
      "end_time": 212482.0,
      "text": "paid a 2.2 million-dollar settlement to the government just last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212506.0,
      "end_time": 215863.0,
      "text": "because it had been collecting second-by-second information"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 215887.0,
      "end_time": 219355.0,
      "text": "about what millions of people were watching on TV, including us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219379.0,
      "end_time": 223840.0,
      "text": "and then it was selling that information to data brokers and advertisers."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 223108.0,
      "end_time": 226330.0,
      "text": "SM: Ah, classic surveillance economy move."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 226775.0,
      "end_time": 230641.0,
      "text": "The devices Kashmir bought almost all pinged their servers daily."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230665.0,
      "end_time": 233600.0,
      "text": "But do you know which device was especially chatty?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 233850.0,
      "end_time": 234379.0,
      "text": "The Amazon Echo."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 234403.0,
      "end_time": 236831.0,
      "text": "It contacted its servers every three minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 236855.0,
      "end_time": 239530.0,
      "text": "regardless of whether you were using it or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 239770.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "KH: In general, it was disconcerting"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 241284.0,
      "end_time": 244268.0,
      "text": "that all these devices were having ongoing conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 244292.0,
      "end_time": 245918.0,
      "text": "that were invisible to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 245942.0,
      "end_time": 248529.0,
      "text": "I mean, I would have had no idea, without your router."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 248553.0,
      "end_time": 252210.0,
      "text": "If you buy a smart device, you should probably know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 252450.0,
      "end_time": 254155.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to own the device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 254180.0,
      "end_time": 257600.0,
      "text": "but in general, the company is going to own your data."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 257624.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260196.00000000003,
      "text": "And you know, I mean, maybe that&#39;s to be expected --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 260220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263727.0,
      "text": "you buy an internet-connected device, it&#39;s going to use the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 264189.0,
      "end_time": 266310.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s strange to have these devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 266550.0,
      "end_time": 268713.0,
      "text": "moving into the intimate space that is the home"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 268737.0,
      "end_time": 272180.0,
      "text": "and allowing companies to track our really basic behavior there."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 272204.0,
      "end_time": 273363.0,
      "text": "SM: So true."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 273387.0,
      "end_time": 276926.0,
      "text": "Even the most banal-seeming data can be mined by the surveillance economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 276950.0,
      "end_time": 279525.0,
      "text": "For example, who cares how often you brush your teeth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 279549.0,
      "end_time": 283750.0,
      "text": "Well, as it turns out, there&#39;s a dental insurance company called Beam."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 283990.0,
      "end_time": 286933.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been monitoring their customers&#39; smart toothbrushes since 2015 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 286958.0,
      "end_time": 289537.0,
      "text": "for discounts on their premiums, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 289561.0,
      "end_time": 291820.0,
      "text": "KH: We know what some of you are thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291844.0,
      "end_time": 294498.0,
      "text": "this is the contract of the modern world."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294522.0,
      "end_time": 295949.0,
      "text": "You give up a little privacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 295973.0,
      "end_time": 299191.0,
      "text": "and you get some convenience or some price breaks in return."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299514.0,
      "end_time": 301855.0,
      "text": "But that wasn&#39;t my experience in my smart home."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301879.0,
      "end_time": 305553.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t convenient, it was infuriating."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 305577.0,
      "end_time": 308690.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll admit, I love my smart vacuum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 308930.0,
      "end_time": 310498.0,
      "text": "but many other things in the house drove me insane:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 310522.0,
      "end_time": 312918.0,
      "text": "we ran out of electrical outlets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 312942.0,
      "end_time": 316321.0,
      "text": "and I had to download over a dozen apps to my phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 316345.0,
      "end_time": 317672.0,
      "text": "to control everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317696.0,
      "end_time": 319785.0,
      "text": "And then every device had its own log-in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 319809.0,
      "end_time": 322172.0,
      "text": "my toothbrush had a password ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322196.0,
      "end_time": 323933.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 323957.0,
      "end_time": 328850.0,
      "text": "And smart coffee, especially, was just a world of hell."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 328109.0,
      "end_time": 332370.0,
      "text": "SM: Wait, really? Cloud-powered coffee wasn&#39;t really working for you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 332610.0,
      "end_time": 335299.0,
      "text": "KH: I mean, maybe I&#39;m naive, but I thought it was going to be great."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 335323.0,
      "end_time": 339342.0,
      "text": "I thought we&#39;d just wake up in the morning and we&#39;d say, \"Alexa, make us coffee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 339366.0,
      "end_time": 341239.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not how it went down."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 341263.0,
      "end_time": 345914.0,
      "text": "We had to use this really particular, brand-specific phrase to make it work."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 345938.0,
      "end_time": 350546.0,
      "text": "It was, \"Alexa, ask the Behmor to run quick start.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 351222.0,
      "end_time": 354563.0,
      "text": "And this was just, like, really hard to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 354588.0,
      "end_time": 355922.0,
      "text": "first thing in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 355946.0,
      "end_time": 357649.0,
      "text": "before you have had your caffeine."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 357673.0,
      "end_time": 358776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 358800.0,
      "end_time": 360490.0,
      "text": "And apparently, it was hard to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 360514.0,
      "end_time": 363577.0,
      "text": "because the Echo Dot that was right next to our bed"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 363601.0,
      "end_time": 365212.0,
      "text": "just couldn&#39;t understand us."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 365704.0,
      "end_time": 370325.0,
      "text": "So we would basically start every day by screaming this phrase at the Echo Dot."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 370349.0,
      "end_time": 371522.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 371546.0,
      "end_time": 373120.0,
      "text": "And Trevor hated this."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 373339.0,
      "end_time": 375870.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d be like, \"Please, Kashmir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 375111.0,
      "end_time": 378780.0,
      "text": "just let me go to the kitchen and push the button to make the coffee run.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 379379.0,
      "end_time": 381466.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d be like, \"No, you can&#39;t!"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 381490.0,
      "end_time": 383899.0,
      "text": "We have to do it the smart way!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 383923.0,
      "end_time": 385839.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 385863.0,
      "end_time": 388906.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m happy to report that our marriage survived the experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 388930.0,
      "end_time": 390490.0,
      "text": "but just barely."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 390514.0,
      "end_time": 392561.0,
      "text": "SM: If you decide to make your home smart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 392585.0,
      "end_time": 395433.0,
      "text": "hopefully, you’ll find it less infuriating than Kashmir did."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 395458.0,
      "end_time": 397545.0,
      "text": "But regardless, the smart things you buy"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 397569.0,
      "end_time": 400664.0,
      "text": "can and probably are used to target and profile you."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 401141.0,
      "end_time": 404181.0,
      "text": "Just the number of devices you have can be used to predict"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 404205.0,
      "end_time": 405627.0,
      "text": "how rich or poor you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 405651.0,
      "end_time": 408418.0,
      "text": "Facebook&#39;s made this tech, and they&#39;ve also patented it."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 408442.0,
      "end_time": 412128.0,
      "text": "KH: All the anxiety you currently feel every time you go online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 412152.0,
      "end_time": 413457.0,
      "text": "about being tracked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 413482.0,
      "end_time": 415783.0,
      "text": "is about to move into your living room."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 415807.0,
      "end_time": 417386.0,
      "text": "Or into your bedroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 417950.0,
      "end_time": 420171.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s this sex toy called the We-Vibe."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 420577.0,
      "end_time": 423244.0,
      "text": "You might wonder why a sex toy connects to the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 423268.0,
      "end_time": 426703.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s for two people who are in a long-distance relationship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 426728.0,
      "end_time": 429648.0,
      "text": "so they can share their love from afar."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 430259.0,
      "end_time": 432375.0,
      "text": "Some hackers took a close look at this toy"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 432399.0,
      "end_time": 434474.0,
      "text": "and saw it was sending a lot of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 434498.0,
      "end_time": 436960.0,
      "text": "back to the company that made it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 436984.0,
      "end_time": 439950.0,
      "text": "when it was used, how long it was used for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 439974.0,
      "end_time": 443680.0,
      "text": "what the vibration settings were, how hot the toy got."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 443704.0,
      "end_time": 445893.0,
      "text": "It was all going into a database."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 445917.0,
      "end_time": 448666.0,
      "text": "So I reached out to the company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 448690.0,
      "end_time": 451992.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"Why are you collecting this really sensitive data?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 452369.0,
      "end_time": 455755.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"Well, it&#39;s great for market research.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 456592.0,
      "end_time": 459520.0,
      "text": "But they were data-mining their customers&#39; orgasms."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 459545.0,
      "end_time": 461466.0,
      "text": "And they weren&#39;t telling them about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 461490.0,
      "end_time": 463712.0,
      "text": "I mean, even if you&#39;re cavalier about privacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 463736.0,
      "end_time": 466331.0,
      "text": "I hope that you would admit that&#39;s a step too far."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 466680.0,
      "end_time": 469188.0,
      "text": "SM: This is why I want to keep my sex toys dumb."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 469212.0,
      "end_time": 470378.0,
      "text": "KH: That&#39;s great."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 470402.0,
      "end_time": 472680.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all very glad to know that."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 472920.0,
      "end_time": 473539.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 473564.0,
      "end_time": 475598.0,
      "text": "SM: A data point I&#39;m willing to share."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 475622.0,
      "end_time": 477345.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 477369.0,
      "end_time": 480339.0,
      "text": "The devices Kashmir bought range from useful to annoying."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 480363.0,
      "end_time": 482156.0,
      "text": "But the thing they all had in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 482180.0,
      "end_time": 484879.0,
      "text": "was sharing data with the companies that made them."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 484903.0,
      "end_time": 487211.0,
      "text": "With email service providers and social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 487235.0,
      "end_time": 490193.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve long been told that if it&#39;s free, you&#39;re the product."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 490217.0,
      "end_time": 492224.0,
      "text": "But with the internet of things, it seems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 492248.0,
      "end_time": 494256.0,
      "text": "even if you pay, you&#39;re still the product."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 494280.0,
      "end_time": 495525.0,
      "text": "So you really have to ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 495549.0,
      "end_time": 497734.0,
      "text": "Who&#39;s the true beneficiary of your smart home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 497758.0,
      "end_time": 499387.0,
      "text": "you or the company mining you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 499411.0,
      "end_time": 501363.0,
      "text": "KH: Look, we&#39;re a tech savvy crowd here."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 501387.0,
      "end_time": 504499.0,
      "text": "I think most of us know that these things connect to the internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 504523.0,
      "end_time": 505686.0,
      "text": "and send data out."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 505710.0,
      "end_time": 509727.0,
      "text": "And fine, maybe you&#39;re OK with living in that commercial panopticon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 509752.0,
      "end_time": 511149.0,
      "text": "but others aren&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 511173.0,
      "end_time": 514140.0,
      "text": "We need the companies to rethink the design of these devices"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 514380.0,
      "end_time": 515553.0,
      "text": "with our privacy in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 515577.0,
      "end_time": 518688.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re not all willing to participate in \"market research,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 518712.0,
      "end_time": 521605.0,
      "text": "just because a device we bought has a Wi-Fi connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 522140.0,
      "end_time": 523212.0,
      "text": "And I have to tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 523236.0,
      "end_time": 525818.0,
      "text": "even when you&#39;re aware, generally, this is happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 525842.0,
      "end_time": 530236.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s really easy to forget that normal household items are spying on you."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 530664.0,
      "end_time": 533140.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easy to forget these things are watching you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 533380.0,
      "end_time": 535850.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t look like cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 535109.0,
      "end_time": 536538.0,
      "text": "They could look like ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 536562.0,
      "end_time": 539106.0,
      "text": "well, they could look like a dildo."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 539780.0,
      "end_time": 540932.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 540956.0,
      "end_time": 544642.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}